      "content": "i've tried the tools and the support, but nothing fixes the fact that i'm just a net negative in their lives. it's like if you have a wound that won't heal and it keeps infecting everything else around it, eventually you just have to remove it for the sake of the rest of the body. it's not even about me wanting to die, it's just about wanting them to finally have a chance at a life that isn't weighed down by me.",
